			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Origin Debug Book (Ctrl+Shift+7)\r\nAstarion - Recruit - As Avatar (for AOM) or Companion (for COM)\r\nAstarion - Act 3 Origin Moments - Vampire Spawns Duo at Flophouse\r\nWalk in the direction the player character is facing.\r\nClick on Petra or Dalyria."
				},
