				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Dalyria and Petras at the flophouse.\r\nThey are looking for Astarion at the place where they used to \"hunt\".\r\nThis is a dialog for when they meet Astarion-Avatar or Astarion-Companion with the player-Avatar.\r\nThey will tell Astarion they must inform Cazador that Astarion is back in the city. They will also reveal that Cazador is planning a ritual that requires all the spawn and that will grant them new powers.\r\nIf Astarion knows that Cazador is actually planning to sacrifice all the spawn, he might be able to convince the spawn about this sacrifice. In exchange, they will reveal a bit of information about Cazador's Palace.\r\nAfter the dialog, they disappear as clouds of mist."
				}
			}
		}
